genresAdvancedInfo.name: dutch punk rock
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Dutch punk rock is a high-energy, fast-paced genre that combines the raw power of punk with the rebellious spirit of rock. It's characterized by its aggressive guitar riffs, pounding drums, and confrontational lyrics that tackle social and political issues head-on.
